=== 領隊／教練 ===
; 諾定咸森林
2014年3月27日，皮雅斯以家庭原因婉拒接任[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]領隊<ref>{{citenews |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/26766771 |title=Nottingham Forest: Stuart Pearce rules out City Ground return |date=2014-03-27 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714225955/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/26766771 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年4月3日，最終回心轉意，答應於來季7月1日開始正式接掌帥印<ref>{{citenews |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/26867437 |title=Stuart Pearce: Nottingham Forest confirm Reds legend as boss |date=2014-04-03 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2014-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809230949/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/26867437 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年2月1日，諾定咸森林最近7戰6負，聯賽榜位列第12位，皮雅斯被即時免去職務<ref>{{citenews |language =en |url =http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/31085816 |title =Dougie Freedman replaces Stuart Pearce at Nottingham Forest |work =''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date =2015-02-01 |accessdate =2015-02-02 |archive-date =2015-02-02 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150202231852/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/31085816 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。

== 私人生活 ==
1998年8月5日皮雅斯在[[诺丁汉|诺丁汉]]發生交通意外，一輛7[[噸|噸]]貨車在路上翻倒，並壓在皮雅斯所駕駛的[[罗孚_(汽车品牌)|罗孚]]房車的車頂，在[[消防員|消防員]]到場前皮雅斯已自行離開車廂，事後送院檢查只手部輕微擦損及背痛<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/146096.stm |title=Pearce survives collision with lorry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=1998-08-05 |accessdate=2009-04-11 |archive-date=2020-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217230917/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/146096.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。皮雅斯的車是由車廠作為推廣計劃送給[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]的，事後皮雅斯獲罗孚贈送一輛新車作為替補<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/147259.stm |title=Psycho nets new motor after crash |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=1998-08-07 |accessdate=2009-04-11 |archive-date=2020-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217230923/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/147259.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

